er-olivette-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-xavier-olivette-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-xavier-olivette-680x680.jpeg 680w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-xavier-olivette-896x896.jpeg 896w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 1279px) calc(100vw - 26rem), 680px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e \t\t\t\t\u003cfigcaption id=\"gallery-1-2000558684\"\u003e \t\t\t\t© Xavier Olivette, Bandai Namco Filmworks/Khara \t\t\t\t\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e \t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt.jpeg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt.jpeg\" alt=\"Gundam Gquuuuuux Comoli Harcourt\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-1-2000558676\" srcset=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt.jpeg 1200w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-680x680.jpeg 680w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-comoli-harcourt-896x896.jpeg 896w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 1279px) calc(100vw - 26rem), 680px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e \t\t\t\t\u003cfigcaption id=\"gallery-1-2000558676\"\u003e \t\t\t\t© Comoli Harcourt, Bandai Namco Filmworks/Khara \t\t\t\t\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \t\t\u003c/div\u003e  \u003cp\u003eBy 0085, Char is seemingly nowhere to be found—but the Red Gundam, as it’s now dubbed, re-emerges in the Earth Sphere, participating in underground mobile suit battles at the colony \u003cem\u003eGQuuuuuuX\u003c/em\u003e protagonist Machu calls home. As well as new looks at both classic and Zeonic forms of the Gundam RX-78-2—re-imagined by \u003cem\u003eEvangelion\u003c/em\u003e mechanical designer Ikuto Yamashita as something altogether more skeletal and like the frame of a prototype compared to the armored form of the classic aesthetic—the new material also includes a look at the setting’s take on the iconic Zeon grunt suit, the Zaku, given curved armor placements over a similarly skinny internal frame, as well as several intriguing Zeon characters beyond Char himself. Those \u003ca href=\"https://gizmodo.com/gundam-gquuuuuux-challia-bull-newtypes-theory-2000548205\"\u003einclude Challia Bull\u003c/a\u003e, a newtype Zeon officer who appeared in a later episode of the 1979 anime to help set the stage for its exploration of \u003ca href=\"https://gizmodo.com/witch-from-mercury-ending-newtypes-lgbt-suletta-miorine-1850607368\"\u003epsionically enhanced pilots\u003c/a\u003e, and two new young officers of various Zeon military academies, Xavier Olivette and Comoli Harcourt.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe studio also revealed a few more characters who also call the Side 6 colony home that Machu eventually meets as she’s wrapped in the world of “clan battles” in the form of the proprietors of Kaneban Co, a junk dealer acting as a front for recruiting pilots into the underground fight scene—including an \u003cem\u003eadorable\u003c/em\u003e Pomeranian who acts as company mascot, and two little robots, one new (Konch, a cuboid little robot seen in the trailers with Shuji, the new pilot of the Red Gundam), and one very familiar (a Haro, wearing a beanie, the spherical robot who’s been a part of \u003cem\u003eGundam\u003c/em\u003e since the very beginning).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n \u003ch2\u003e\u003cem\u003eMobile Suit Gundam GQuuuuuuX\u003c/em\u003e Colony Characters\u003c/h2\u003e \u003cdiv id=\"gallery-2\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e \t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi.jpeg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi.jpeg\" alt=\"Gundam Gquuuuuux Annqi\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-2-2000558692\" srcset=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi.jpeg 2000w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-680x680.jpeg 680w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-896x896.jpeg 896w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-annqi-1792x1792.jpeg 1792w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1023px) calc(100vw - 2rem), (max-width: 1279px) calc(100vw - 26rem), 680px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e \t\t\t\u003c/p\u003e \t\t\t\t\u003cfigcaption id=\"gallery-2-2000558692\"\u003e \t\t\t\t© Annqi, Bandai Namco Filmworks/Khara \t\t\t\t\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e \t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-jezzi.jpeg\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-jezzi.jpeg\" alt=\"Gundam Gquuuuuux Jezzi\" aria-describedby=\"gallery-2-2000558691\" srcset=\"https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-jezzi.jpeg 1920w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gundam-gquuuuuux-jezzi-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://gizmodo.com/app/uploads/2025/02/gu